# Environment should be switched by commenting either BAS environment or Local VSCode environment. Make sure to comment the other environment.
# Region for comment would be - Start to - End

### BAS environment -- Start
@s4_base_url=http://S4HC_MONITOR_BASIC_AUTH_CUST.dest
@default_headers=Content-Type: application/json
@Accept=Accept: application/json

@svc_url_v2={{s4_base_url}}/sap/opu/odata/sap/API_CREDIT_MEMO_REQUEST_SRV
@svc=http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/monitor

# @name metadata_call

GET {{svc_url_v2}}/$metadata
{{default_headers}}
X-CSRF-Token: Fetch

###
@csrf_token={{metadata_call.response.headers.X-CSRF-Token}}

### Create Credit Memo Request
# @name create_credit_memo_request_call
POST {{svc_url_v2}}/A_CreditMemoRequest
X-CSRF-Token: {{csrf_token}}
{{default_headers}}

